{"word":"κύαθος","slug":"κύαθος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κύαθος</b></el> <el>(κύᾰθος, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κύω'><el>κύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a cup</i>, for drawing wine out of the <el>κρατήρ</el> or bowl, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a cupping-glass</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}